title.en: Otasuke Chara ni Tensei Shita no de, Game Chishiki de Musou Suru ~Unmei wo Nejifusete, Saikyou wo Mezasou to Omoimasu~
Ryuu ni Sodaterareta Saikyou ~Subete wo Kiwameta Shounen wa Ningenkai wo Musou suru~
Hitodasuke wo Shitara Party wo Tsuihousareta Otoko wa, Unique Skill "Otasuke Man" de Nariagaru.
Kono Boukensha, Jinruishi Saikyou desu - Hazura Skill "Kantei" ga "Keishou" ni Kakusei shita no de, Amata no Eiyuu-tachi no Chikara wo Uketsugi Musou suru
Ossan wa Uzeeeen da yo! tte Guild kara Tsuihou Shita Kuse ni, Go kara Fukki Yousei wo Dasarete mo Osoi. Saikou no Nakama to Deatta Ore wa Kocchi de Saikyou wo Mezasu!
Mushoku no Saikyou Kenja ~Job ga Erarezu Tsuihou Saretaga, Game no Chishiki de Isekai Saikyou~
Saitei Chara ni Tensei shita Ore wa Ikinokoritai
Tsuyo Sugite Yuusha Party wo Sotsugyou shita Saikyou Kenshi, Mahou Gakuen demo Aisareru
Kashita Maryoku wa "Ribobarai" de Kyousei Choushuu ~Youzumi to Party Tsuihousareta Ore wa, Kawaii Support Yousei to Issho ni Toritateta Maryoku wo Unyou shite Saikyou wo Mezasu.~
Shokei Sareta Saikyou no Gunnyou Majutsushi, Haisenkoku no Elf Hime to Kokka Saikensu ~Sokoku yo Jama Suru no wa Kattedaga, Sono Majutsu Tsukutta no Ore na Node Kikanai ga?~
Yuusha Party wo Tsuihou Sareta "Skill Supporter," Nakama no Sukiru wo Kaihou Shite Saikyou ni Nariagaru
Raitei to Yobareta Saikyou Boukensha, Majutsu Gakuin ni Nyuugaku shite Issai no Enryonaku Musou suru
Unsouya no Ossan ga Nazeka Fukugyou de Zettai Muteki Kenshi wo Tsutomeru Koto ni: Saenai Jinsei wo Okutteta Ore ga Maou Toubatsu no Kirifuda ni?
Isekai de Cheat Skill wo Te ni Shita Ore wa, Genjitsu Sekai wo mo Musou Suru: Girls Side ~Kareinaru Otome-tachi no Bouken wa Sekai wo Kaeta~
Saiteihen no Ossan Boukensha. Guild wo Tsuihou Sareru Tokoro de Ima made no Doryoku ga Mukuware, Kyuu ni Saikyou Skill "Mujouken Shouri" wo Eru
Kaibutsu-tachi wo Suberu Mono - Saikyou no Shien Tokka Nouryoku de, Kizukeba Sekai Saikyou Party ni!
